  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>The compact cabin style rooms are perfect for those want an active holiday, perfect if you're first and last on the mountain. </p>
<p><strong>Smart Cabins</strong> are compact cabin style rooms, at around 18㎡ sleeping two with a double bed next to a panoramic window. </p>
<p><strong>XL Cabins</strong> are slightly larger at around 23㎡, these rooms sleep up to three people with a double bed and single mattress, there's also a sofa next to the panoramic window which can be made up as a fourth bed.</p>
<p><strong>Family Cabins</strong> are around 27㎡ sleeping four people. These rooms have a double bed and bunk beds next to the panoramic window. </p>
<p><strong>Family Loft Cabins</strong> are set over two floors, sleeping four people. These rooms have a double bed next to the panoramic window and two single beds - perfect for friends and families.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Austrian twin style beds</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>TV with streaming service</li>
<li>Private bathroom with shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Online check-in available</li>
<li>Daily housekeeping is not offered during the week</li>
<li>Cots are not available</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
